[下载地址](http://www.longene.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=4700)

安装:
```
sudo dpkg -i 软件名.deb
```

卸载:
```
先dpkg -l | grep qq 找到名字，然后执行：sudo dpkg -r qq-for-wine 或 sudo dpkg -P qq-for-wine
```

